      "children": [
        {
          "type": "text",
          "text": "时态深化（八种时态）"
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "type": "element",
      "tag": "p",
      "children": [
        {
          "type": "text",
          "text": "现在完成时是学习难点（have/has+过去分词），表示过去动作对现在的影响。标志词 ever/never/already/yet/just/since/for。"
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "type": "element",
      "tag": "p",
      "children": [
        {
          "type": "text",
          "text": "现在完成时和一般过去时的区别：前者强调对现在的影响不涉具体时间，后者强调过去动作涉及具体时间。"
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "type": "element",
      "tag": "p",
      "children": [
        {
          "type": "text",
          "text": "过去进行时 was/were+doing，表示过去某时刻正在进行的动作。常与 when/while 连用。"
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "type": "element",
      "tag": "h2",
      "className": "section-title",
      "children": [
        {
          "type": "text",
          "text": "被动语态"
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "type": "element",
      "tag": "p",
      "children": [
        {
          "type": "text",
          "text": "结构 be+过去分词 (+by+执行者)。一般现在时 am/is/are+done，一般过去时 was/were+done，情态动词 can/must/should+be+done。"
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "type": "element",
      "tag": "p",
      "children": [
        {
          "type": "text",
          "text": "不及物动词 happen/take place/appear 无被动语态。感官动词 feel/sound/taste 用主动表被动。"
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "type": "element",
      "tag": "h2",
      "className": "section-title",
      "children": [
        {
          "type": "text",
          "text": "状语从句"
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "type": "element",
      "tag": "p",
      "children": [
        {
          "type": "text",
          "text": "时间状语从句 when/while/as/before/after/until，条件状语从句 if/unless，主将从现原则。原因状语从句 because/since/as，让步状语从句 although/though（不与but连用）。"
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "type": "element",
      "tag": "h2",
      "className": "section-title",
      "children": [
        {
          "type": "text",
          "text": "核心词汇与短语"
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "type": "element",
      "tag": "ul",
      "children": [
        {
          "type": "element",
          "tag": "li",
          "children": [
            {
              "type": "text",
              "text": "look for/take care of/give up/put on/turn off 等动词短语"
            }
          ]
        },
        {
          "type": "element",
          "tag": "li",
          "children": [
            {
              "type": "text",
              "text": "at first/in fact/by the way/in a hurry 等介词短语"
            }
          ]
        },
        {
          "type": "element",
          "tag": "li",
          "children": [
            {
              "type": "text",
              "text": "not only...but also.../either...or.../neither...nor... 等连词短语"
            }
          ]
        },
        {
          "type": "element",
          "tag": "li",
          "children": [
            {
              "type": "text",
              "text": "be good at/be afraid of/be interested in/be proud of 等固定搭配"
            }
          ]
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "type": "element",
      "tag": "h2",
      "className": "section-title",
      "children": [
        {
          "type": "text",
          "text": "阅读与写作"
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "type": "element",
      "tag": "p",
      "children": [
        {
          "type": "text",
          "text": "skimming（略读）获取大意，scanning（扫读）定位细节。阅读先看题目再读文章，带着问题更高效。"
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "type": "element",
      "tag": "p",
      "children": [
        {
          "type": "text",
          "text": "写作结构主题句+支撑细节+总结句。使用连接词 first/second/finally/however/therefore 使文章更流畅。"
